{"tid":2146061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"時事評論員馮智政：被美方制裁官員可與中資銀行交易","createTime":"2020-08-08T10:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T11:15:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9fdbcdbdedbcb0268e54871840ee1126551fc3","tid":2146061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542591-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542591-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=491a6b53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542591-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=84312155\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542591-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n時事評論員馮智政相信，美資銀行以及在美國有主要業務的其他外國銀行，不會再同被制裁的官員進行交易，有關官員可以同中資銀行交易。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook公司證實，被列入制裁名單的Facebook帳戶，將被禁止使用任何存在支付行為的服務。香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑相信，相關個人帳戶或社交專頁，不能付費落廣告，即「贊助帖文」。"},{"pid":"4c8322f469e4c999969a6d06cda570daed2f0039","tid":2146061,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"馮智政個樣原來咁鳩"},{"pid":"8923e9aab9475ae5e1cea18e1ecce1ccad06c445","tid":2146061,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"中資銀行唔怕被美國制裁咪同SDL人仕服務囉"},{"pid":"554391998b7429a32439d3a8af9b26e8ab0e31d9","tid":2146061,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">不能為幾個被制裁的人，拖垮整個香港百年金融基業。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n試以以上題目作文，500字。"},{"pid":"3fb2066b63beb5cdcc383d650629fb7d6d4bc988","tid":2146061,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"染金髮都好毒"},{"pid":"47a9814e8849b9a4b8bd2ee5fea62b188a005e7